        {
            "type": "h1",
            "text": "How to use Honorific Converter"
        },
        {
            "type": "body",
            "text_items": [
                {
                    "styles": [],
                    "text": "Honorific Converter is a support application for creating sentences in honorifics (keigo, 敬語), which is difficult even Japanese people.\nBy writing or pasting Japanese sentences, it automatically revise incorrect sentences.\n\nHonorific Converter has three tabs: \"Convert\", \"Generate\" and \"Articles\"."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "h2",
            "text_items": [
                {
                    "styles": [],
                    "text": "About \"Convert\" tab"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "body",
            "text_items": [
                {
                    "styles": [],
                    "text": "You can convert to the next five honorifics.\n\n"
                },
                {
                    "styles": [
                        "respectful"
                    ],
                    "text": "Respectful"
                },
                {
                    "styles": [],
                    "text": " - Words to respect the other party\n"
                },
                {
                    "styles": [
                        "humble"
                    ],
                    "text": "Humble I"
                },
                {
                    "styles": [],
                    "text": " - Words that humble yourself and respect the other party\n"
                },
                {
                    "styles": [
                        "courteous"
                    ],
                    "text": "Humble II"
                },
                {
                    "styles": [],
                    "text": " - Words to humble yourself (no connotation of respect)\n"
                },
                {
                    "styles": [
                        "polite"
                    ],
                    "text": "Polite"
                },
                {
                    "styles": [],
                    "text": " - Civility like 'please'\n"
                },
                {
                    "styles": [
                        "polite"
                    ],
                    "text": "Bikago"
                },
                {
                    "styles": [],
                    "text": " - Add \"お\" or \"ご\" or \"御\" to the beginning of a noun. In most cases, this is also civility like 'please'\n"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "block_quote",
            "text_items": [
                {
                    "styles": [],
                    "text": "明日の午後1時にあなたの会社に行きます。\nI will go to your office at 1pm tomorrow."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "body",
            "text_items": [
                {
                    "styles": [],
                    "text": "First, change \"あなたの会社\" (your office) to the "
                },
                {
                    "styles": [
                        "respectful"
                    ],
                    "text": "Respectful"
                },
                {
                    "styles": [],
                    "text": " \""
                },
                {
                    "styles": [
                        "respectful"
                    ],
                    "text": "貴社"
                },
                {
                    "styles": [],
                    "text": "\".\nAnd \"行く\" (go to) is yourself action, so change it to "
                },
                {
                    "styles": [
                        "humble"
                    ],
                    "text": "Humble I"
                },
                {
                    "styles": [],
                    "text": " or "
                },
                {
                    "styles": [
                        "courteous"
                    ],
                    "text": "Humble II"
                },
                {
                    "styles": [],
                    "text": "."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "block_quote",
            "text_items": [
                {
                    "styles": [],
                    "text": "✅ 明日の午後1時に"
                },
                {
                    "styles": [
                        "respectful"
                    ],
                    "text": "貴社"
                },
                {
                    "styles": [],
                    "text": "に"
                },
                {
                    "styles": [
                        "humble"
                    ],
                    "text": "伺います"
                },
                {
                    "styles": [],
                    "text": "。"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "block_quote",
            "text_items": [
                {
                    "styles": [],
                    "text": "✅ 明日の午後1時に"
                },
                {
                    "styles": [
                        "respectful"
                    ],
                    "text": "貴社"
                },
                {
                    "styles": [],
                    "text": "に"
                },
                {
                    "styles": [
                        "courteous"
                    ],
                    "text": "参ります"
                },
                {
                    "styles": [],
                    "text": "。"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "body",
            "text_items": [
                {
                    "styles": [],
                    "text": "Next,"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "block_quote",
            "text_items": [
                {
                    "styles": [],
                    "text": "先週の土曜日に京都に行きました。\nI went to Kyoto last Saturday."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "body",
            "text_items": [
                {
                    "styles": [],
                    "text": "In this case, the other party is not involved in the action of \"行く\", so changing it to "
                },
                {
                    "styles": [
                        "humble"
                    ],
                    "text": "Humble I"
                },
                {
                    "styles": [],
                    "text": " is a mistake, use "
                },
                {
                    "styles": [
                        "courteous"
                    ],
                    "text": "Humble II"
                },
                {
                    "styles": [],
                    "text": "."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "block_quote",
            "text_items": [
                {
                    "styles": [],
                    "text": "❌ 先週の土曜日に京都に"
                },
                {
                    "styles": [
                        "humble"
                    ],
                    "text": "伺いました"
                },
                {
                    "styles": [],
                    "text": "。"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "block_quote",
            "text_items": [
                {
                    "styles": [],
                    "text": "✅ 先週の土曜日に京都に"
                },
                {
                    "styles": [
                        "courteous"
                    ],
                    "text": "参りました"
                },
                {
                    "styles": [],
                    "text": "。"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "body",
            "text_items": [
                {
                    "styles": [
                        "polite"
                    ],
                    "text": "Polite"
                },
                {
                    "styles": [],
                    "text": " and "
                },
                {
                    "styles": [
                        "polite"
                    ],
                    "text": "Bikago"
                },
                {
                    "styles": [],
                    "text": " have no such rule."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "h2",
            "text_items": [
                {
                    "styles": [],
